# CBT Architecture

- Single Next.js codebase inside Electron — no separate backend project.
- Business logic in `src/services/`, data access in `src/repositories/`, thin API handlers in `src/app/api/`.
- SQLite via Prisma for V1; schema must remain PostgreSQL-migration-compatible.
- Server is source of truth for exam timers, submission, and grading.
- Use `src/lib/db.ts` Prisma singleton — never instantiate PrismaClient elsewhere.
- Domain types and constants live in `src/modules/`; mock data in `src/data/mock/` until Phase 2.
